  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Assist Local Indigenous Farmers in Southern Belize</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ya&apos;axche Conservation Trust focuses part of its work on helping local, small-scale farmers in southern Belize transition to more sustainable farming practices. Not only does this help farmers improve their income and food security, it also helps the environment by reducing deforestation and sustaining the health of soils and watersheds.  Through this funding we will be able to provide direct support to the local farmers that we work with, such as a technical visit, seedlings, or farm tools.</narrative>
  </description>
